  "stem": "<p><math><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn></math></p><p><math><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>7</mn></math></p><p>Which ordered pair <math><mfenced><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>y</mi></mrow></mfenced></math> is a solution to the given system of equations?</p>",
